    },
    {
      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "For an aging lab with weight concerns, you'll want a balanced profile, but aim for a ratio that leans towards higher protein while managing fat intake. Look for a protein percentage in the range of 28% to 35% on the guaranteed analysis. Keep the fat content moderate, ideally below 18%, to help manage weight without sacrificing essential nutrients. It's always best to check the specific brand's recommendations for senior dogs, as individual needs vary.",
